{"tid":301894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反恐特勤隊大火力長槍進駐會展     警三步一崗防恐襲","createTime":"2017-06-29T03:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T10:29:08.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3685ad5faf1962c2b96ac6a8aef7c95020842ec5","tid":301894,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170629/large/1498706045_ea28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170629%2Flarge%2F1498706045_ea28.jpg&h=7eec624a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170629/large/1498706125_21dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170629%2Flarge%2F1498706125_21dc.jpg&h=de406b97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170629/large/1498706222_2be0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170629%2Flarge%2F1498706222_2be0.jpg&h=2cbfda9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170629/large/1498706318_bfe8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170629%2Flarge%2F1498706318_bfe8.jpg&h=71ca2465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平料最快今日黃昏抵達會展，會展及君悅一帶保安提升到最高級別，以確保領導人安全。今晨記者在灣仔中環廣場接連會展的行人天橋，見到有反恐特勤隊警員荷槍實彈，配備最新式及火力強大的瑞士製SIG 516 CQB 半自動步槍駐守及巡邏，警犬亦有出動執勤。<br />\n<br />\n而進入會展廣場門內，更設有兩個安檢站，有警員手持掃描棒，普通市民可以隨意進內，但記者經過安檢時，警員並未有檢查記者隨身物品，商場內的銀行及一間售賣朱古力的商店繼續營業，但毗鄰售賣酒類的店舖則暫停營業。<br />\n會展範圍內亦有多重保安及警員駐守，除工作人員外，一律均不得進入，至於習總入住的君悅酒店，亦是除相關人員外，不能內進。接連海景萬麗的入口亦已封閉，被兩重鐵欄圍封。<br />\n會展地面有過百名穿著西裝制服，掛上「工作人員證」的人員，經過工作分配後散去各司其職，而會展外港灣道有一批警員，正整理鎖車工具。"},{"pid":"0d9acc0e5dbfbbdcbe88ed75af3a584a29330457","tid":301894,"uid":3117,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:37:30.000Z","msg":"驚咩恐襲呀 直接話驚香港人 港獨咪得囉"},{"pid":"e5661f167d3e549e2b2df97863382730f4187671","tid":301894,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:38:33.000Z","msg":"有長火冇避彈衣"},{"pid":"bff809d9097212553a807821ecf023afbcb68f74","tid":301894,"uid":33787,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"473a899198e587a902e549fdf98a5fbea9e96e61","tid":301894,"uid":32028,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:39:57.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人知佢幾點到, 今晚機, 我怕又搞到封路封機場"},{"pid":"ce7ab583b6fb66e324b165b40638a819b177cd23","tid":301894,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有冇人知佢幾點到, 今晚機, 我怕又搞到封路封機場</blockquote><br />\n中午到"},{"pid":"ff5e81864a77fc3c55f7d3846f3d30a36b43d3f7","tid":301894,"uid":33787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c660b441bcedbc57b807cd129d5da5cde51884f8","tid":301894,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:41:51.000Z","msg":"小心走火"},{"pid":"a980b377022f7ffa64ff74087c04d58f086e1ffd","tid":301894,"uid":36035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f53111038bbac8a45c7691bdd5e94beb95e0c6a","tid":301894,"uid":55043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訂晒一間酒店成個星期要幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n你敢收爛仔錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b38a6daca86e5e9135d97f071bc56afc4b5926","tid":301894,"uid":55043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>驚咩恐襲呀 直接話驚香港人 港獨咪得囉</blockquote><br />\neast turkestan疆獨、isis</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撚入到黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"